To determine the exchange rate from China to Britain, I need to convert Chinese Yuan (CNY) to British Pound (GBP). I will use the `exchange_for_currency_v2` function to get the current exchange rate.

### Step 1: Get the Exchange Rate
I will call the `exchange_for_currency_v2` function with the base currency as CNY and the target currency as GBP.

#### Function Call
```json
{
  "name": "exchange_for_currency_v2",
  "parameters": {
    "base": "CNY",
    "to": "GBP"
  }
}
```
